{"tid":1974154,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"牛市之油價係好快會上番，因為中東馬上大亂","createTime":"2020-04-15T15:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T19:56:07.000Z","uid":40478,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4acb1232ecae40d68eadbbf6017b3aaa7d6e253c","tid":1974154,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gN899L5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgN899L5.png&h=a63735af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n直接copy阿拉伯之春既Wiki比大家睇<br />\n劇本係咪好熟口熟面呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有今年油價跌得更劇烈，國際環境更差（因為頁岩油令美國能源可以自給，中東穩定唔再係美國核心利益）<br />\n同最最重要既係今年東非-中東一帶有沙漠蝗蟲大爆發，目前估計6月高潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食物缺乏就會暴亂，中東既石油供應過剩問題好快會得到解決，樓主估計最遲一年內就可以睇到呢件事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（更更重要係面面只係9up，無真係入到油股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"c051a96a5fdce99722db2028625d764063ffe2a6","tid":1974154,"uid":85803,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持"},{"pid":"3345d2fb32b058dfa68c44e1b9450166daf2453f","tid":1974154,"uid":172031,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:58:35.000Z","msg":"咁岩我諗緊點解傾完 OPEC, 油就有 $29 回到 $19, 牛兄就出佐文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDo you still remember me~<br />\n<br />\n明明係因為油價太賤先由美方促使沙俄去埋位傾野"},{"pid":"b385488874438db8b2d4c8a1fab8f91fcfd37c24","tid":1974154,"uid":40478,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3345d2fb32b058dfa68c44e1b9450166daf2453f","tid":1974154,"uid":172031,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:58:35.000Z","msg":"咁岩我諗緊點解傾完 OPEC, 油就有 $29 回到 $19, 牛兄就出佐文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/